summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and amending Section 2-18 of Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, to rezone a portion of the South one-half of the Southwest one-quarter of the Southeast one-quarter of Section 20, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M., located on the west side of 10th Avenue North, between East Garfield Street and East Blaine Street.
